summary: Changes MAK07´s Remodeled armors Elven armor, new CBBE body and skirt.
descriptionHtml:
Please keep in mind... the skirt is short and there are no panties :)

You´ll need MAK07´s mod for this found here:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13004

Either install it or get the file, it contains some textures you´ll need for the belt.

The skirt comes from Skimpy Elven armor found here:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12796

This is just something I was playing with since I´m at home with a sick kid :þ

Full credit goes to MAK and Wiftody for their mods.
Elven retexture can be found here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23125
author: Laxi2610
